<br>
-Bug fixes<br>
<br>
Malos overwrites chant of venom.  Any non-bard slow overwrites Largo's.<br>
<br>
-Song Changes<br>
<br>
-Make Dirge of Metala 10 tick duration.  Add a small dot component (like assonance) to prevent too much abuse.<br>
<br>
AA Ideas<br>
<br>
-Create a 3 rank AA that adds a tick of duration to songs that already last longer than 3 ticks.  Make it work for clicked items as well. Start with one extra tick per rank minimum to songs that lasted 4 ticks, up to something like an extra minute on 2.5 mins selo's.<br>
