<br>
With two EB procs from DoN camps I can hold agro off of an Anguish rogue, the cleric healing me, and just about anyone who doesn't taunt (and warriors with BBoB). The only thing lacking is snap agro, which we have been told wont be given to us.<br>
<br>
Songs droping wont be fixed. Its been an issue since the original EQ and the developers have yet to figure out a way to resolve this problem because the synch between server and client cannot be improved upon given the current state of high speed technology. <br>
<br>
Further more I agree with you that we should drop those 4 issues from the list. SoE wont forget about them any more then they have already. Rather I should say SoE wont change their stance on the issue. They have a clear idea of what a bard does, and those four issues aren't key to that idea.<br>
