<br>
*Befallen – First floor door (11)<br>
*Befallen – Third floor door (between 12 and 100)<br>
*Cablis – Shaman guild door (201)<br>
*Charasis – All locks (200/201)<br>
*Chardok – Royal’s area (201)<br>
*City of Mist – Entrance door (200/201)<br>
*City of Mist - Elevator door (&lt;100)<br>
*City of Mist – Upper level areas (200/201)<br>
*Freeport/East – Basement door in Hallard’s Resales (124)<br>
*Freeport/North - Door in bank (201)<br>
*Highkeep - Locked door on 4th floor (unpickable)<br>
*Howling Stones - all locks (200/201)<br>
*Karnor –Venril Area (200/201 skill)<br>
*Najena – Two doors to Rathyl’s room (&lt;100)<br>
*Najena - Jail Cell (&gt;125)<br>
*Paineel – Entrance to Paineel (&lt;100)<br>
*Paineel – Entrance to Hole (&lt;100)<br>
*Seblis – All locks (201)<br>
*Ssraehza Temple – All locks (201)<br>
*Thurgadin - Basement door (unpickable)<br>
*Tower of Frozen Shadow – Exit from 4th floor &amp; exit from 7th floor (&lt;100)<br>
<br>
Pretty sad when you go to help someone trapped in Najena, only to find out that you can't pick the lock and you have to give them a gate potion... <p>&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.crimsontalon.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;<br>
