<br>
A base of 1500 (times 4.2 = 6300, crits for twice that) is too big for a non-nuking class. In fact, a crit for 12k would beat out my wizard friend's biggest crit, he has his 70 nuke, and a 10k crit is big for him. <br>
<br>
If it had a 300-350 base (1260-1470) that's a respectable amount of burst damage, considering that we can cast it three times in nine seconds. With a reasonable mana cost of 1k say, would give an outlet for our mana pool on raids where not much else happening but the big beat down.<br>
<br>
I don't think bards will get root, but a 30-second snare would be nice. Or just fix dirge to be fixed duration. And fix VoV to be twistable, don't give us another song to make up for the first ones inadequies.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://p201.ezboard.com/btheconcerthall.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tenille>Tenille</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#330000>(6/27/05 3:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=20156.topic&index=24>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bard Top 10 Issue List - Starting From Scratch</span><hr size=1> dsavereide: Something like <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=742&source=Live">this song</a> ? <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=314700" target="top">Tenille Dia`mond</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
